<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink349">
<l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
<l>porikāṉ māñciṉai putaiya</l>
<l>verikā liḷantaḷi rīṉum poḻutē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t he himself come? The season has arrived,  </l>
<l>that gives birth to young sprouts that shine like fire, </l>
<l>to hide branches of mango tree with parched trunk.  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
